summary: A young female nordic preset for RaceMenu.
descriptionHtml:
[center][/center]Hello,
This is a preset of Roxane, a young nordic female, fighting for Ulric.
And this is my first contribution for the Skyrim Nexus.
I hope you like her!

[b]Step 1 - Requirements :[/b]
[url=http://skse.silverlock.org/]SKSE[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624]RaceMenu
[/url]
Step 2 - Mods recommended :

Body and face texture : [b][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35267/?]SG Female Textures Renewal[/url][/b]

Hair : [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/10168]ApachiiSkyHair[/url] 
Brows : [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35327/?]SG Female Eyebrows[/url]
Eyes : [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/]The Eyes Of Beauty[/url]
Lips : [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/22701/?]Seductive Lips HD[/url]
Make up : [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/31665/?]Better Makeup for SKSE[/url]
ENB : I use the [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/42957/?]Mistveil[/url] preset in my screenshoots. Other ENB are nice too.

NB : She has a beauty spot, but i don't remember from what mod it comes.

Step 3 - How to install

If you have RaceMenu version 3 or higher :
Copy the file Nord_Roxane.jslot here : Skyrim\Data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen\Presets
Go into showracemenu
Go on the preset tab
Hit F9 for load the preset. 
Choose the preset Nord_Roxane.jslot

If you have an ancient version of RaceMenu :
Copy the file 23.slot here : Skyrim\Data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen\Presets
Go into showracemenu
Set race to Nord and load the preset Slot 23 (Hit F9 to load the preset.)
I put size at 0.97 or 0.98.

Enjoy!
